<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal"><font style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="line-height: 17.12px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="background-color: white;">Hi {!Lead.FirstName},<br></span></span></font><br><font face="Arial, sans-serif">I’ve been trying to contact you to provide a business insurance quote but unfortunately, I’ve not heard from you.<br><br>We know you're busy, so we want to take one last opportunity to remind you of&nbsp;<b>your exclusive 10% discount as a Book a Builder customer</b>.&nbsp;</font><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br></span><br><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Given we've not been able to contact you, we'll now be closing your file. However, if you want to move forward with a quote at any time,<span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span></font><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><a href="https://calendly.com/d/cn2r-pc5-kc5/kingsbridge-insurance-call-back-book-a-builder">book a call with me</a></b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">.</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp;<br><br></span><b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Not able to answer calls during the day?</span></b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Send me a message on WhatsApp using&nbsp;<b><a href="https://go.kingsbridge.co.uk/bab-ar-whatsapp">07917 515428</a></b>&nbsp;and I’ll contact you via message instead.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Alternatively, let me know the best date and time for me to call you or give me a ring on&nbsp;</span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808 740</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>All the best!<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>{!User.FirstName}&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Sales Team<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>E: salesteam@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><font style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">T:&nbsp;</font><font style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808740</font></p>]]></td>
